quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  40,41,"“Yemwe bantu banjye! Kuki mbahamagarira kurokoka, mwe mukampamagarira kugana umuriro?”"
  40,42,"“Murampamagarira guhakana Allah ngo mubangikanye n’ibyo ntafitiye ubumenyi? Nyamara njye ndabahamagarira kugana (Allah) Nyirimbaraga zihebuje, Ubabarira ibyaha.”"
  40,43,"“Nta gushidikanya ko ibyo mumpamagarira nta cyo byamarira mu byo nabisaba, haba ku isi cyangwa ku mperuka, kandi igarukiro ryacu ni kwa Allah. Kandi abarengera imbago (za Allah) ni bo bantu bo mu muriro.”"
  40,44,“Kandi muzibuka ibyo mbabwira! Nanjye ibyanjye mbyeguriye Allah! Mu by’ukuri Allah ni Ubona abagaragu be mu buryo buhebuje.”
  40,45,"Nuko Allah amurinda imigambi mibisha yabo bari bagambiriye, maze ibihano bibi bigota abantu ba Farawo"
  40,46,"Umuriro bawushyirwamo mu gitondo na nimunsi (aho bari mu mva zabo), n’igihe umunsi w’imperuka wageze (abamalayika bazabwirwa bati): “Nimwinjize abantu ba Farawo mu bihano (umuriro) bikaze cyane.”"
  40,47,"Kandi (zirikana) ubwo bazatongana bari mu muriro (baterana amagambo), maze abanyantege nke babwire ba bandi bibonaga (ku isi) bati “Mu by’ukuri ni mwe twakurikiraga. Ese none hari icyo mwatumarira, mu kutugabanyiriza kuri ibi bihano by’umuriro?”"
  40,48,Ba bandi bibonaga (ku isi) bazavuga bati “Rwose twese tuwurimo! Mu by’ukuri Allah yamaze gukiranura abagaragu be.”
  40,49,Nuko abari mu muriro bazabwire abarinzi ba Jahanamu bati “Nimudusabire Nyagasani wanyu atugabanyirize ibihano kabone n’ubwo byaba umunsi umwe.”